    "In general, motivation refers to an internal urge that forces us to do something.",
    "Within the framework of teaching and learning English, it is what encourages us to learn and teach English.",
    "Wu (2013) argued that one of the key factors determining the achievement of learners in learning a language was motivation.",
    "The results of the research study, conducted to investigate the factors affecting the use of vocabulary, revealed many factors including family involvement and teacher encouragement.",
    "However, it was found that motivation had the greatest effect."
